# Copy to `.dev.vars` for local development (git-ignored). `wrangler`/`vite dev`
# load this automatically.
#
# Bearer token that gates POST /api/insert-games and /api/purge-cache. The seed
# script (scripts/insert-games.sh) defaults to this value for --local runs.
# In production set it as a secret instead: `wrangler secret put PURGE_SECRET`.
PURGE_SECRET="local-dev-purge-secret"
